# Golem-Powers Skills Environment Template
# ==========================================
# Use `op inject` to populate this template with 1Password secrets:
#   op inject -i skills/.env.template -o skills/.env
#
# Or use `op run` to inject and run a command:
#   op run --env-file=skills/.env.template -- your-command
#
# Vault structure:
#   - development: Global dev tools (context7, tempmail, anthropic)
#   - Private: Personal keys (GitHub PAT, claude-golem item)
#   - Cantaloupe: Union/work project secrets
#   - Domica: Domica project secrets
#
# Setup: See README.md "Skills Environment Variables" section

# Anthropic - Claude API access
# Required by: Various AI-powered skills
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=op://development/ANTHROPIC_API_KEY/credential

# Context7 - Library documentation lookup
# Required by: golem-powers:context7
CONTEXT7_API_KEY=op://development/context7/API_KEY

# Linear - Issue tracking integration
# Required by: golem-powers:linear, golem-powers:worktrees
# Note: Get your API key from Linear > Settings > API > Personal API Keys
LINEAR_API_KEY=op://development/LINEAR_API_KEY/credential
